{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm05_event05","chara":[{"id":105101}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"Dolma, how are you doing...?@I'm, well, the same as always.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":105101,"motion":200}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"If you're reading this letter..."},{"chara":[{"id":105101}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"It means the Lama delivered it to you properly,@didn't he?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":105101,"motion":1}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"...That's good."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":105101}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"Hmm... What should I write?"},{"chara":[{"id":105101,"motion":100,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"There are so many things I want to say, to convey,"},{"chara":[{"id":105101}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"but the words don't come out right..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":300,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"Yes... Should I write about the past?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":105101}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"From the very beginning..."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_19303.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":833800,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"On the night when our hometown was@attacked by the Mongolian Army...@I was holding your trembling hand as we@fled from the Mongols, right?","narrationBg":"bg_adv_19303.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameCenter":"Lama","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"Oh...@You two..."},{"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"It was at that time that I met the Lama,@who served as the Rector at the nunnery,@and we escaped unscathed...","narrationBg":"bg_adv_19303.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"...The Lama had heard rumors about me@and was heading to our hometown."},{"narration":"They wanted to train me at the nunnery...@thinking I was some special being capable@of performing miracles."},{"narration":"...Well,@I wasn't quite the way the Lama expected..."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"black","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_033.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"Yes...@I returned to our hometown in secret that@night and witnessed that horrifying scene.@I felt defeated.","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"You know, they were calling me a savior and@expected me to save our hometown from@the Mongolian Army, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":105101,"motion":300}],"narration":"But I couldn't do anything, and our@hometown was burnt to the ground...@Everyone except us died..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":105101}],"narration":"...I was completely crushed,@understandably so..."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_63011.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833800,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story03","chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"Heruka, Dolma...@Have you gotten used to life at the nunnery?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"Uh... Well..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":1,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Heruka","textRight":"...We've only been here for a short while,@so it's not easy to get used to."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":833800,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"I see.","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833800,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"However...@You must get accustomed to it."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"You both are here to receive training."},{"chara":[{"id":105101,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Heruka","textRight":"...Training for what?"},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"Training to become Rakshasi."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"Rakshasi...@Is that about Heruka...?"},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"I know that Heruka was called Rakshasi@in our hometown."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"...If was after you survived a landslide, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"It's not just that... She saved me..."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"Yes, that's right...@Dolma was also caught in the landslide."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"Thanks to Heruka, you were saved from a@dire situation..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Heruka","textRight":"It was just a coincidence, really..."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"...It might indeed have been a coincidence."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"But in the end, you saved a life."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"Even when our hometown was attacked again@this time, you survived..."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"And saved another life."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":833800,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"...You have potential."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"You are special."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"Oh..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":105101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Heruka","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833800,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"The people of our hometown believed in you@as the savior who could perform miracles"},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"and called you Rakshasi."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"But that was just what they decided@on their own..."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"To truly become a Rakshasi,@a proper ritual is necessary."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Heruka","textRight":"...A ritual?"},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"Yes, you will receive training here to@undergo that ritual."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"Training..."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"Don't worry, there are many others here."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":833800,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"Everyone, you can come in now."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833800},{"effect":"fadeout","id":833300}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Junior Nun","textLeft":"[live2dName:live2d_0:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]Yay, which one is Heruka?"},{"chara":[{"id":833900}],"nameRight":"Junior Nun","textRight":"[live2dName:live2d_1:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]You must have amazing talent, right?@I'm so jealous!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1"}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833800,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"Heruka","textRight":"Who are these people...?"},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"They are junior nuns aspiring to@become Rakshasi."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Heruka","textRight":"...Junior nuns?"},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"They are treated differently from regular monks,@but well, you don't need to worry about it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":833800,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Lama","textLeft":"Essentially...they're your new friends."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833800},{"effect":"fadeout","id":105101}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":2}],"nameCenter":"Junior Nuns","textCenter":"Nice to meet you!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1"}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":1,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"...H-Heruka, what should we do...?"},{"chara":[{"id":105101,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"What do you mean?"},{"chara":[{"id":833300}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"I mean...@Should we run away...?"},{"chara":[{"id":833300,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"If you don't want to become a Rakshasi,"},{"chara":[{"id":833300}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"we don't have to stay here..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":105101,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"..."},{"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"Either way, we have no place to go,@so let's follow the customs here...","narrationBg":"bg_adv_63011.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"That way, at least Dolma can live safely..."},{"narration":"At that time, I decided to live at the nunnery,@thinking about such things."},{"bgm":"stop","narration":"Little did I know that I would be swept into@a great whirlpool from there..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
